Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.17,0:00:05.83,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m going to put on an amazing performance during summer break!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:07.10,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Huh!?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.79,0:00:14.28,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Megu-chan would never miss a performance from the Hasunosora School Idol Club!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.77,0:00:20.89,Rurino,,0,0,0,,To motivate Megu-chan, I decided that I’d have to work hard on myself first!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:29.82,Rurino,,0,0,0,,So I figured that the best way to light a fire in her heart would be to do a special summer performance!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:31.70,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Nice, Rurino-chan…!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.45,0:00:35.49,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I think that’s a great idea!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:37.30,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Isn’t it!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.84,0:00:40.26,Kozue,,0,0,0,,A live performance, huh?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:42.26,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I agree.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:43.58,Kozue,,0,0,0,,However…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:48.50,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It will be considerably difficult doing a live performance so soon after joining the club, even for you.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:52.36,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Doubly so if you aim to move someone’s heart.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:58.59,Rurino,,0,0,0,,That just means I’ll need our veterans to bring on lots of special training!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:00.20,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Oh…?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.27,0:01:02.77,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Special, you say...?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:08.05,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You can’t just say things like that to Kozue-senpai, Rurino-chan!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.05,0:01:09.53,Kaho,,0,0,0,,She’ll squeeze you dry, you know!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.53,0:01:13.59,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Your dried flower has certainly flourished, wouldn’t you say, Kaho-san?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.06,0:01:14.89,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Eek…!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:16.13,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Hey.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:19.74,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,What is it, Tsuzuri-senpai?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.13,0:01:21.23,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Do you need a nap?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:23.12,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,No?\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:25.32,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,What am I to you?\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:27.32,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:29.28,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I want us to do a training camp.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.73,0:01:30.56,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Training camp…?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:34.90,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Last year, we talked about maybe going to the beach.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:36.52,Kaho,,0,0,0,,The beach!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.06,0:01:40.33,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:43.51,Kozue,,0,0,0,,The plan ended up falling through, though.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.51,0:01:45.23,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’m surprised you remember.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.09,0:01:46.62,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:53.04,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Since then, every day I wondered when we would go to the beach.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:54.18,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I see…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:58.55,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,She’s almost like a little girl waiting for a letter from Santa…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.19,0:02:02.21,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Huh!? The beach!? I wanna go to the beach!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:04.36,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You too, right, Rurino-chan!? Right!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:05.63,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:12.86,Rurino,,0,0,0,, Listening to the raging tides in total solitude on a winter’s beach is the best!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:16.14,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Wait, that’s not what I was thinking of at all!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:18.07,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Gah-... Um…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:23.06,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But, well… Even if the beach ends up being completely filled with people…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:24.56,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I still wanna do a training camp!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:27.60,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Um… will you be okay with that?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:28.73,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,It’s just…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:32.60,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I expect you might have to spend a lot more time with other people than normal,\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:34.45,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,so you might run out of battery…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:36.55,Rurino,,0,0,0,,It’ll probably happen!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:37.54,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Huh!?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:42.90,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But I’m doing all of this for Megu-chan,\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:45.31,Rurino,,0,0,0,,so even if it might happen, I still wanna do it!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:49.02,Rurino,,0,0,0,,For the Megu-chan Flaring Fire Plan…!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:55.03,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Oh… but maybe I might end up causing trouble for everyone…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:03:00.54,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ll do everything I can to make sure I don’t end up becoming a water flea, so…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:06.09,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Kozue-senpai, Tsuzuri-senpai, I’m leaving it all up to you!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:08.85,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Please train me well!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:13.98,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Very well, leave it to me.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:19.19,Kozue,,0,0,0,,This summer, all of us will hold a training camp.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:22.20,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yay!!! Beach time!!!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:27.91,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,T-This is very nice, right, Tsuzuri-senpai?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:30.81,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You’ve had to wait a year for this…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:33.87,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,…Wait.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:37.43,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,If we’re going to hold a training camp, does that mean…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:42.91,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I’ll have to look after her the whole time…? {\fad(0,260)}\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:49.77,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Training camp!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:51.38,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Beach!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.03,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,B-Babysitting…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:05.04,Megumi,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong with me…?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.47,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I can do it in practice, but…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:10.47,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Megumi.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:14.79,Megumi,,0,0,0,,…Ugh.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:17.09,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Kozue, Tsuzuri, what is it?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:20.99,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Whatever our relationship might be right now, I don’t think it warrants an “ugh.”\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:24.92,Kozue,,0,0,0,,You watched our recent performance, didn’t you?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:28.72,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Aren’t you interested in how Rurino-san is doing?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:33.99,Megumi,,0,0,0,,No? I don’t have anything to do with the School Idol Club anymore.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:37.92,Megumi,,0,0,0,,What she does is none of my business.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:41.81,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Ruri’s gonna be performing solo next time.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.26,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Huh!? Isn’t it way too soon for that!?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:49.70,Megumi,,0,0,0,,She wouldn’t have the stamina for it, so she ought to do more foundational training…!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:51.38,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Ah.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:56.36,Megumi,,0,0,0,,B-But it’s not like I care about that or anything!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.74,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It’s what Rurino-san wanted.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:03.21,Kozue,,0,0,0,,She said that she needed to show a certain someone her performance, no matter what.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:05.21,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Hm…?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:07.31,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Hey, Megu.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:11.72,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Kozu and I performed together.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:13.72,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Seems so.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:22.27,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,We made a promise to each other when we decided to retire from Nationals, right?\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:28.36,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,That we would never be involved with each other ever again.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:36.16,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,You even said that you didn’t want to waste our time on your rehab.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:39.46,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I didn’t say it like that.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:41.95,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Huh? You did, though.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:45.01,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Gh–... Um…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:47.86,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,She said so, right, Kozu?\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:52.95,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I remember her forcing a smile even though she looked like she was about to cry.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.32,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,“You guys don’t need to–”\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:56.60,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Okay, enough already! Why are you doing this!?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:58.90,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Do something, Kozue!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:04.32,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Since you’ve been gone, I’ve had to deal with Tsuzuri on my own.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:07.02,Megumi,,0,0,0,,And I’m sorry about that!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:09.88,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Wait, no! I don’t have to apologize for that!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:12.86,Megumi,,0,0,0,,What are you two even here to say!?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:15.61,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Well, in short…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:17.77,Kozue,,0,0,0,,That was a year ago.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:23.41,Kozue,,0,0,0,,And we have already broken that promise the three of us made.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:27.60,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Hmph… and you’re deciding that for me.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:29.92,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Either way, I can’t do it.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.19,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’m… I’m still…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:34.29,Kozue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Megumi.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:39.73,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember us talking about going on a training camp session at the beach before?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:42.10,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Eh? When was this...?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:45.88,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Why don’t you come with us next week?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:49.52,Megumi,,0,0,0,,…Huh!?  \N{\fs40}[Megumi]
